177 A.3d 129 MUSTAFA MUHAMMAD, PLAINTIFF-PETITIONER, v. ALLEN SELTZER AND EXTRA STORAGE SPACE, DEFENDANT-RESPONDENT.

C-428 September Term 2017

078839 December 13, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002275-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
